channel.title: Need help fast
channel.description:
Hi yeasterday moparscape did work now when i click on it it come a bit in the loading and then it say Sorry,an error has occured whilst loading runescape
to fix this try the following (in order):
1:Try closing ALL open web-browser windows,andreloading (this i have done)
2:Try clearing your web-browsers cache from tools->iternet options (this have i done)
3:Try using a different game-world (moparscape got no different gameworld i think)
4:Try rebooting your computer (this have i done)
5:Try selecting a different version of java from the play-game menu (wath it mean with that ?)
(this did happen after i need to re-install moparscape)
Plz i need fast answer.
I think this came from normal rs when it are error there
